{
  "stem": "1160.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and there were-- the rest of the train, there was such a-- also, this was a good part of the train, you know, with seats and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were cattle trains, a lot of trains there, the same train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were a lot of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and in this part already, everybody was going on their own way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So my mother and the children are alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We aren't-- we have nobody there anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember anybody there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five of us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those solders are there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they are laughing, the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we are saying that we wanna go up, up to the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were saying in Russian, Jews!",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were from the train, kicking, like to go away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they didn't let us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then my next picture what I see in my head again, that we are sitting-- I don't know how we got on there-- it's the same train or some other one.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we are not sitting on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are sitting-- you know how you connect the trains together, those big things, how you-- I don't know how you call those-- almost like pipes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Locks or what-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Locks, and it has a flat part.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to-- you know, they go together, and you chain them together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- we are sitting on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On that we arrived to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how I arrived at Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Budapest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Budapest--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Budapest we arrived, and there a man came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started to touch us-- head, hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he started to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother says, he's crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't talk to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, he was told that no children are survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
